From 5a29daedeb5ac7e9e2af87ce1a7bbfad230d5c86 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Michael Han <hanm@apache.org>
Date: Mon, 24 Jul 2017 10:39:45 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] ZOOKEEPER-2792 ZOOKEEPER-1045: Port implementation from
 branch-3.4 to branch-3.5.

This pull request implements SASL based server to server authentication and authorization based on the code changes made as part of ZOOKEEPER-1045 to branch-3.4. All unit tests (minors the known flaky ones) should pass now.

The main obstacle of the ports is code base difference between branch-3.4 and 3.5 with major new features (e.g. dynamic reconfiguration). The port itself does not add new features - i.e. how servers with authenticate with each other with the presence of dynamic reconfiguration. That work will be covered by a separate pull request targeting ZOOKEEPER-2793 and ZOOKEEPER-2794.

Author: Michael Han <hanm@apache.org>

Reviewers: Rakesh Radhakrishnan <rakeshr@apache.org>

Closes #272 from hanm/ZOOKEEPER-2792

